# User Directives — ${STUDIO_NAME}

**These tasks are DIRECTIVE ORDERS from the studio owner. They are NOT negotiable.**
- PM does NOT evaluate these with RICE/ROI — they are immediately APPROVED.
- PM writes specifications for them into `product_requirements.md` as `[DIRECTIVE]` items.
- Senior Developer treats them as highest priority — ahead of all R&D-generated tasks.

## How to Add a Directive
Write a new section below the line with this format:

### D-<N>: <Title>
- **Domain:** ${DOMAINS}
- **Description:** What to do, as clearly as possible
- **Priority:** IMMEDIATE (default) | after <X> | when available
- **Acceptance Criteria:** How we know it's done
- **Date Added:** YYYY-MM-DD

